<Author>mmbi
<Content>Great hotel with excellent service The Embassy Suites is located at Paseo Reforma. The historical centre of Mexico City is a 20 minutes walk or a short taxi ride away. Except for the steakhouse in the hotel itself, there are only few restaurants in the immediate neighborhood of the hotel, but the restaurants of Zona Rosa can be reached within a few minutes.The hotel is new, the two-room suite was very large, nicely decorated, clean and quiet. Flat-screen LCD TVs are provided in both rooms. Wireless internet access is available in the rooms. The bathroom was spacious and clean, and free bottled water is provided each day.The staff was extremely friendly and efficient. The excellent breakfast buffet with made-to-order omelettes is included in the room rates.The Embassy Suites is well worth the price, in particular compared to other four-star hotels in the area. I would definitely stay there again. 
