<Author>CamasFrank
<Content>4-5 Star Excellence Adding to what has already been written, this is an brand new, high quality property that has still to be discovered. Differences vs regular Embassy Suites:1) Extensive Breakfast: local fruits  foods; chef makes a great huevos rancheros2) Beautiful basement pool, spa and fitness room3) Highly efficient staffed business center: fast and professional help with color and b/w printing4) Concierge that arranged excellent local car service (vans @ 200P/hour)5) Extremely high quality room construction and amazing beds/linnens/pillows6) Managers reception that includes liquor7) A handy-dandy Starbucks in the lobby.8) High-end bar/restaurant attached (didn't try it)Location is central and 10 minutes from Polanco.I highly, highly recommend it to business travelers as a lower price but same/higher quality than Polanco. I have stayed at the Intercontinental Presidente and this property blows it away.Paid $189/US for a Premier Room: large window, large table for work. 
